Robert Rabiah https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Rabiah 0 Robert Rabiah is an Australian film actor best known for his roles as Hakim in Face to Face, Nick in Chopper, Dario Mancini in Fat Tony Co., Spiro Politis on TV soap Neighbours, Mehmet in Deadline Gallipoli, Mohsen in Ali's Wedding, Bilal in Safe Harbour and Sami Almasi in Secret City (TV series).
